'''Operation Emperor's Spear''' was a battle tactic used by [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]] and the [[Insiders]] at the [[Battle of Borleias (Yuuzhan Vong War; Second)|Battle of Borleias]] during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]]. Because the [[Executor-class Star Dreadnought/Legends|''Executor''-class Star Dreadnought]] ''[[Lusankya/Legends|Lusankya]]'' had already taken severe damage in the defense of [[Borleias/Legends|Borleias]], it was decided that she would be used in a final suicide mission against the [[Koros-Strohna|worldship]] in command of all [[Yuuzhan Vong]] forces in the [[Pyria system]]. The plan involved installing a giant reinforced lance into the center of ''Lusankya'', filling it with explosives and ramming the ship into the [[Domain Hul worldship]].

The Star Dreadnought had long before had its weapons subtly and systematically stripped and donated to smaller ships, including [[Booster Terrik]]'s ''[[Errant Venture/Legends|Errant Venture]]''. [[Commander/Legends|Commander]] [[Eldo Davip]], the ''Lusankya''{{'s}} commanding officer, successfully steered the bow of the vast warship toward its target, piercing it deep into the enemy worldship's hull. He managed to escape from the ship shortly before the collision via a [[BTL Y-wing starfighter/Legends|Y-wing]] stored in a nearby shuttle bay. The force of the resulting detonation was so great that it utterly destroyed both the Yuuzhan Vong ship and the ''Lusankya'' herself.

